longBusinessSummary: Newbury Pharmaceuticals AB (publ) operates as hybrid pharmaceutical company in Sweden and the Scandinavian market. The company offers oncology, rare diseases, neurology, and other treatment products. Newbury Pharmaceuticals AB (publ) was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
